title: 'The Walking Dead' Season 6 Plot News: A Fan Favorite Might Die
text: 'The Walking Dead' Viewer Numbers Dip 00:50 The zombies on "The Walking Dead" may be starting to stagger. The Nielsen company said an estimated 14.6 million viewers watched the season premiere of the hit AMC series on Sunday. That's down from the 17.3 million who saw last year's season opener and the 16.1 million people who watched in 2013. ... You Might Like
